00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:45,140
我确实希望这书与众不同
I did want the book to be different,

509
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:48,120
但我  只是觉得这样可能...
but I... It just seems that that might--

510
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:50,840
我觉得这可能是我这些年写得最好的东西了
I think it might be the best thing I've written in years.

511
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:54,610
当然也可能是彻头彻尾的垃圾
It could also be utter and complete shit.

512
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:58,350
但我看不出是好是坏  这一般是好兆头
But when I can't tell the difference, it's usually a good sign.

513
00:27:00,490 --> 00:27:03,560
我只是希望不要偏离了大方向
I just don't want to lose sight of the bigger goal.

514
00:27:03,760 --> 00:27:05,340
我只会这么写
I don't know any other way to write it.

515
00:27:07,710 --> 00:27:08,840
如果这样不合你的意
If you want something different,

516
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:11,630
最好现在就换人
now's the time to find somebody else.

517
00:27:11,630 --> 00:27:13,160
不  我希望你写完
No, I want you to finish it.

518
00:27:15,170 --> 00:27:16,180
虽然我不知道
Even though I have...

519
